Configuration for parallel divided adjoint run.
-----------------------------------------------
o nPx*nPy = 2*2
o nTimeSteps = 240
o makefile is for adjoint code generation 
  (uses additional TAF options -pure -mpi)
o tested on IBM SP4, bluesky.ucar.edu,
  compared to single-proc. DIVA and non-DIVA on sea.mit.edu,
  w.r.t. taf-1.5.0
